\f0\fs24 \cf0 \b Age:\b0  58\
\
\b Appearance:\b0  Small and sturdy, with silver-streaked auburn hair pinned loosely. Reading glasses on a beaded chain. Wears linen in summer, wool in winter. Ink-stained fingers.\
\
\b Background:\b0  Born in Sainte-Barbe, never left. Inherited the bookshop from her aunt at thirty and has run it ever since. Widowed young; no children. Known by everyone in the village as a keeper of stories and secrets alike.}